{"tid":1419091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斥警無通知 辯方：睇新聞才知旺角清場被告提堂","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:35:01.000Z","uid":41343,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"295aca1e37a589f500e41e46b2c17396a36985bc","tid":1419091,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:43:08.000Z","msg":"多名旺角清場被告上周六被捕，昨日首度出庭應訊。有辯方大律師在庭外透露，當事人遭扣留兩天其間，法律團隊「從來冇收過警察任何通知」，前一刻才知道案件提堂，致電警方核實時，45分鐘內未有警員接聽，「打埋去分區指揮官都無人聽」，質疑此情况下「點樣確認疑犯嘅權益唔受侵犯？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n代表被告劉偉麟的大律師石書銘昨日開庭前向控方投訴，他是在案件提堂前一刻才獲通知，質疑警方是否藉此阻止疑犯接觸法律代表。石書銘在庭外說，其法律團隊案發後曾清楚向警方表示，若劉偉麟遭正式落案「麻煩通知一聲」，又稱「做咗咁多年，警察不嬲都好合作」，但他於昨午1時半才透過新聞報道知道提堂消息，即使他立刻致電警署，電話響了45分鐘都沒人接聽，「甚至打埋去分區指揮官都冇人聽」，最後要致電律政司高級助理刑事檢控專員才確認消息。<br />\n<br />\n查詢扣押 警答：唔知喎<br />\n關於上周六黃大仙警方清場，石書銘說當時有被捕人委託他代表，其法律團隊隨即致電黃大仙警署查詢當事人是否正在警署扣留，「由半夜3點打到6點幾」，惟警方只回答「唔知喎」、「資訊好混亂」及「幫唔到你喎」。<br />\n<br />\n石說，若律師不能及時接觸疑犯，擔心警察可以任意妄為。<br />\n<br />\n就石書銘的投訴，警察公共關係科至截稿前仍未有回覆本報。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190806/s00001/1565030059755/%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E7%84%A1%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9-%E7%9D%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%89%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565030059755%2F%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E7%259D%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E6%2589%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=876cf4f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190806%2Fs00001%2F1565030059755%2F%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E7%259D%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E6%2589%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582&h=bedff0fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190806/s00001/1565030059755/%E6%96%A5%E8%AD%A6%E7%84%A1%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9-%E7%9D%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%89%8D%E7%9F%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82</a>"},{"pid":"62dbc502ee06ad1011964fa2f56f43a42d0ac9f3","tid":1419091,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:44:02.000Z","msg":"合理理由可以申請壓後,唔係架咩"},{"pid":"24c114f1b4479bc523caa073891104e102428082","tid":1419091,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:44:30.000Z","msg":"有名你叫黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90193ba09fb90cdf223547042167a8c165e0948c","tid":1419091,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:52:28.000Z","msg":"警犬真係幾on9<br />\n特登咁早俾位人入打程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef05d22ecc51111126766340f21133929743c128","tid":1419091,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90193ba09fb90cdf223547042167a8c165e0948c","tid":1419091,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:52:28.000Z","msg":"警犬真係幾on9<br />\n特登咁早俾位人入打程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:07:57.000Z","msg":"唔戇鳩就唔會考警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfbf84034444a66f9b7fcc6d87a7eb66ffce729","tid":1419091,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:10:12.000Z","msg":"仆街黑警想靜雞雞搞掂班義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2716a01a4ec6f9e71f152760288ba74e2f19dd69","tid":1419091,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot